  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Seven Days of an Artist and a Girl</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive seven days with a cursed painting. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The protagonist, trapped in a gloomy studio for seven days, must contend with a cursed painting of a girl to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1321120/extras/187ed14853e22f17c080a367cec9d484.poster.avif?t=1774316450\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1321120/extras/187ed14853e22f17c080a367cec9d484.webm?t=1774316450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1321120/extras/187ed14853e22f17c080a367cec9d484.mp4?t=1774316450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rely on notes from past victims and manage to successfully paint her portrait.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But be careful not to upset her, or you'll quickly find yourself dead!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1321120/extras/0a3be5abafe5e5486dd3708f3b74f921.poster.avif?t=1774316450\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1321120/extras/0a3be5abafe5e5486dd3708f3b74f921.webm?t=1774316450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1321120/extras/0a3be5abafe5e5486dd3708f3b74f921.mp4?t=1774316450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An assortment of terminal tableaus awaits you. Will you be the one to finally finish her? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Be aware that this game contains some horror elements. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*There are no jump scares or heart-pounding scenes, so you can rest easy as you play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*There are no puzzles involving codes or searching for keys, unlike usual escape games. There is only the mystery of the girl.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1321120/extras/0a8430ea332465313b3eb9ac2da0ea9d.poster.avif?t=1774316450\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1321120/extras/0a8430ea332465313b3eb9ac2da0ea9d.webm?t=1774316450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1321120/extras/0a8430ea332465313b3eb9ac2da0ea9d.mp4?t=1774316450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Remake Elements</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optimized the vertical layout for smartphones to a horizontal layout.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improved user experience with features like message skipping.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1321120/extras/c4071739e98aa171c9c6eeeb7b35f835.poster.avif?t=1774316450\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1321120/extras/c4071739e98aa171c9c6eeeb7b35f835.webm?t=1774316450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1321120/extras/c4071739e98aa171c9c6eeeb7b35f835.mp4?t=1774316450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Added new episodes featuring the girl in the painting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1321120/extras/36e3743819c4646ab36e13de94c74428.poster.avif?t=1774316450\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1321120/extras/36e3743819c4646ab36e13de94c74428.webm?t=1774316450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1321120/extras/36e3743819c4646ab36e13de94c74428.mp4?t=1774316450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Seven Days of an Artist and a Girl</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive seven days with a cursed painting. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The protagonist, trapped in a gloomy studio for seven days, must contend with a cursed painting of a girl to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1321120/extras/187ed14853e22f17c080a367cec9d484.poster.avif?t=1774316450\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1321120/extras/187ed14853e22f17c080a367cec9d484.webm?t=1774316450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1321120/extras/187ed14853e22f17c080a367cec9d484.mp4?t=1774316450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rely on notes from past victims and manage to successfully paint her portrait.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But be careful not to upset her, or you'll quickly find yourself dead!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1321120/extras/0a3be5abafe5e5486dd3708f3b74f921.poster.avif?t=1774316450\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1321120/extras/0a3be5abafe5e5486dd3708f3b74f921.webm?t=1774316450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1321120/extras/0a3be5abafe5e5486dd3708f3b74f921.mp4?t=1774316450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An assortment of terminal tableaus awaits you. Will you be the one to finally finish her? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><