b_paragraph\" >Added new episodes featuring the girl in the painting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1321120/extras/36e3743819c4646ab36e13de94c74428.poster.avif?t=1774316450\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1321120/extras/36e3743819c4646ab36e13de94c74428.webm?t=1774316450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1321120/extras/36e3743819c4646ab36e13de94c74428.mp4?t=1774316450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
